			"baseEffect": "<p><strong>Cantrip · 1 Action · Range 8 · Single Target.</strong></p><p><strong>Damage:</strong> 1d4. You may move the target 1 space instead of damaging them. <strong>On crit:</strong> you may Blind them instead (until the end of their next turn).</p><p><em>Forced Movement.</em> Small/Tiny targets can be moved twice as far; Large, half as far (round down); creatures bigger than that cannot typically be subject to forced movement.</p>",
